Words can't describe the amount of  gratitude I have for my past 4 seasons as a Los Angeles Laker Girl 💛🏀💜 

Dancing in the purple & gold for the greatest fans in the world has been a dream come true...✨ I will forever cherish the friendships, memories, and once in a lifetime experiences I gained from my time as a Laker Girl. From dancing for 20,000 people every night, to traveling the world, to even winning the 2020 championship I feel so blessed to have been apart of so many historical sports moments and cheered for one of the most legendary teams in the world @lakers 🙌

Thank you to everyone who made my experience as magical as it was and to my friends and family for your constant love and support 🥹🥹🥹 
I can't wait to see what comes next for me...💫
